![Former investor update template.](/images/blogimages/oldtemplatev3.png){: .shadow}

Knowing that investors can only dedicate a few minutes to each email, I knew that
I had to organize the sections and copy in a way that would increase comprehension
and reading speed, so I employed UX copy techniques.

